headlines: 2022 World Cup semi-finals confirmed, France take on Morocco, while Argentina face Croatia
texts: Will it be back-to-back triumphs for France? One step further for 2018 runner-up Croatia? The last shot at glory for Lionel Messi's Argentina? Or the ultimate fairytale ending for Morocco?

texts: Several firefighters from the Central Fire Station, where Go was posted, were also seen standing in silence in front of the statue in their uniforms as a mark of respect, for around a minute.

headlines: 'Terrible' situation at Ice Magic festival as visitors dressed for -15°C queue for 3 hours outdoors
texts: A Mothership reader observed that many children in the queue were dressed in winter clothes and were "sweating profusely". The reader shared that she and her toddler eventually gave up queuing and left as the queue was not moving.

headlines: S'pore police negotiator once spent 21 hours convincing man not to jump off 7-storey high crane
texts: In 2021, the Crisis Negotiation Unit responded to 65 incidents that involved suicide attempts to barricaded individuals. CNU officers are police officers and psychologists who volunteer their time and hold secondary appointments as negotiators, over and above their primary duties.

headlines: Here’s how I put together a Christmas party for my dogs, all without leaving the house
texts:
In the spirit of the holiday season, our writer organised a Christmas party for her three dogs.
She ordered canine and human-friendly food and treats — with everything delivered right to her doorstep. Cutest pictures and GIFs of the trio included inside.
Brought to you by Grab.

headlines: Argentina beats Netherlands on penalties, will face Croatia in 2022 World Cup semi-finals
texts: The Netherlands came back from a two-goal deficit, with goals in the 83rd minute and in extra time, but Argentina eventually prevailed.

headlines: Separated for 6 years, S'porean man flies domestic helper's 2 children here for surprise reunion
texts: The employer spent S$3,000 of his own money to make this happen. It was the first time the helper's two children have taken a trip out of their own country. And it was the first time in six years the two children have met their mother face-to-face.

headlines: Brazil out of 2022 World Cup after losing to Croatia on penalties

texts: 19-year-old Corporal Edward H Go is the first firefighter to have fallen during an SCDF operation.

headlines: NParks receive alert about crocodile spotted near West Coast Park
texts: These native reptiles can grow to more than 5m in length. NParks is monitoring the area and will continue to keep a close watch on the situation for public safety.
